      "raw_text": "E. G. Mcfarland, formerly of the\nSpokane schools, has been appointed\ndeputy by County Superintendent of\nSchools Watkins. The superintendent\nis holding off arrangements for the\nteachers institute until after the\nmeeting of the county superintend-\nents of the state at Olympia on the\nlast three days Of pep,emoer, when\nhe expects to secure distinguished\ninstructors for Spokane."
